data.description: DELAND: GREAT PRICE for a 4 BEDROOM HOME!! Do not miss out on this 4 bedroom 2.5 bathroom 2 story home in the quaint neighborhood of The Highlands. Open floorplan living with lots of natural light. The kitchen offers views to the backyard and lots of counter and storage space. There is a 1/2 bathroom downstairs for convenience. Upstairs holds the more private areas with bedrooms and full guest bathroom. The Master bedroom has a private EnSuite bath and large walk in closet. The inside Laundry room is conveniently located upstairs as well. The fenced backyard has room to entertain, play and even for a pool! This home is located on the west side of Deland close to shopping, restaurants and the Award winning Downtown. Easy access to the truck route 15A which fast tracks your connection to I4 ramp as well as International Speedway to go the the beaches. Don't wait-Make your appointment today to see all this home has to offer you!
